{"tid":1102900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影印變洩私隱？錯本淪試筆紙　顧客資料「冇格」任睇","createTime":"2019-04-12T05:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T05:39:24.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"960768de6b93405a21c7cb7f79c8387adbf2c67b","tid":1102900,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"影印變洩私隱？錯本淪試筆紙 顧客資料「冇格」任睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U8eMF3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U8eMF3&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=d410bc89\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U8eMF3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190412/photo/bkn-20190412123327371-0412_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190412125823\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190412%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190412123327371-0412_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190412125823&h=5910d16e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬一畀有心人拎咗去用&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n私隱何價？近日坑口有文具店誤將客人的身份證及銀行卡副本當作試筆紙，個人資料慘被其他顧客任睇，不少街坊怒斥離譜。<br />\n<br />\n有網民周四（11日）在Facebook群組「將軍澳」發貼指，她經過坑口一間文具店時，發現試筆紙背面竟印有他人的身份證和銀行卡，當中的個人資料沒有被遮掩，可以任人翻閱。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者即時向店員反映，勸喻不要再使用有關紙張。她又提醒街坊，即使印錯個人資料，亦要自行撕毀影印本，保障自己。<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，不少網民批評涉事文具店：「咁嚴重嘅錯都可以犯」、「點解可以咁冇常識㗎」、「冇用應該即場碎咗佢」，有人諷刺謂：「環保到呢」。"},{"pid":"ec5fd8aef77b8935317d8d70d885413e499b77a9","tid":1102900,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"960768de6b93405a21c7cb7f79c8387adbf2c67b","tid":1102900,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"影印變洩私隱？錯本淪試筆紙 顧客資料「冇格」任睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U8eMF3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U8eMF3&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=d410bc89\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U8eMF3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190412/photo/bkn-20190412123327371-0412_00822_001_01p.jpg?201904